"<div class=\"announce instapaper_body md\" data-path=\"README.md\" id=\"file\"><article class=\"markdown-body entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\"><h1><a href=\"#js-animate\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-js-animate\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>js-animate</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/gaggle/js-animate\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7c8d301ab2a5ea59af362f16fd08622892032f01/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f676167676c652f6a732d616e696d6174652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\" alt=\"Build Status\" data-canonical-src=\"https://travis-ci.org/gaggle/js-animate.svg?branch=master\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://coveralls.io/github/gaggle/js-animate?branch=master\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ca440c41867f05d090f54074b5829e5dadfcde6f/68747470733a2f2f636f766572616c6c732e696f2f7265706f732f6769746875622f676167676c652f6a732d616e696d6174652f62616467652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\" alt=\"Coverage Status\" data-canonical-src=\"https://coveralls.io/repos/github/gaggle/js-animate/badge.svg?branch=master\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>Very simple js-based animation. Based on <a href=\"http://jsfiddle.net/LzX4s/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://jsfiddle.net/LzX4s/</a>, I just switched to Promises and added tests.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"#to-install\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-to-install\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>To install:</h3>\n<pre><code>npm install gaggle/js-animate\n</code></pre>\n<h3><a href=\"#simple-example\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-simple-example\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Simple example:</h3>\n<pre><code>var animate = require(\"js-animate/animate\")\n\nanimate({\n  duration: 1000,\n  step: function (delta) {\n    element.style.opacity = delta\n  }\n})\n</code></pre>\n<h3><a href=\"#includes-various-easing-functions\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-includes-various-easing-functions\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Includes various easing functions:</h3>\n<pre><code>linear, quadratic, swing, circ, back, bounce, elastic\n</code></pre>\n<h3><a href=\"#and-convenience-functions\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\" id=\"user-content-and-convenience-functions\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>And convenience functions:</h3>\n<pre><code>var opacity = require(\"js-animate/opacity\")\nopacity.fadeOut(element, {duration: 1000})\n  .then(function () {\n    return opacity.fadeIn(element)\n  })\n</code></pre>\n</article></div>"